properties.title: representative
properties.name: Fred Keller
properties.biography: Fred Keller, a Representative from Pennsylvania; born in Page, Coconino County, Ariz. graduated from Shikellamy High School, Sunbury, Pa., 1984; graduated from Don Paul Shearer Real Estate School, Wormleysburg, Pa., 1985; business manager; business owner; member of the Pennsylvania state house of representatives, 2010-2019; elected as a Republican to the One Hundred Sixteenth Congress, by special election, to fill the vacancy caused by the resignation of United States Representative Thomas A. Marino
